# .NET Code Style

Full standard: [docs/dotnet-code-style.mdc](../../docs/dotnet-code-style.mdc)

On conflict with routing/layout, [.cursor/rules/minimal-api-migration.mdc](minimal-api-migration.mdc) wins.

**Quick checks (Phase 7 — after 7.4):**
- Run **`dotnet-format`** skill immediately after writing code (step 7.4)
- Run **`dotnet-unit-tests`** skill at step 7.5 (Cobertura + TRX for Azure DevOps)
- File-scoped namespaces; prefer `record` for DTOs/commands
- Minimal APIs — thin endpoints, logic in `Infrastructure/Services/`
- `dotnet format` clean; warnings as errors where configured
- If Native AOT is enabled, also apply `aot-safety.mdc` and run `aot-compat-check` in 7.7
